text: The Aérospatiale SA-321 Super Frelon is a transport and ASW helicopter designed and built in France. The design was first built by Sud Aviation, and later by Aérospatiale. It's built under chineses licence like Avicopter AC313. Some were used by Israel and South Africa. == References == Category:French military aircraft Super Category:Helicopters
title: Aérospatiale SA-321 Super Frelon
